## Administrative Controls

### Customer Data Correction

- Update customer name, contact details, or address.

---

### Payment Correction

- Reverse incorrect payments.
- Ensures accurate financial records.

---

### Cancel Booking

- A booking can only be canceled after payment reversal.
- Maintains data and financial consistency.

---

## Security Features

- Secure login system  
- Role-based access  
- Row Level Security (RLS) at database level  
- Protection of sensitive burial and financial data  

---

## Best Practices

- Always verify grave selection before booking  
- Ensure accurate customer information entry  
- Record payments immediately  
- Use reports regularly for monitoring  
- Perform corrections carefully to maintain data integrity  

